{
  "video_id": "50yxXTAHrfc",
  "title": "How Argentina's blind soccer team became champions (with English subtitles) | Gonzalo Vilari√±o",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14630.0,
      "end_time": 16230.0,
      "text": "I opened a blind man&#39;s head."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17363.0,
      "end_time": 21837.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t make him think or reflect -- I cracked his head open, literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22564.0,
      "end_time": 24969.0,
      "text": "We were walking with him holding onto my shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24993.0,
      "end_time": 27833.0,
      "text": "I miscalculated how much space there was between us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27857.0,
      "end_time": 29622.0,
      "text": "and I knocked him into a gate."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29646.0,
      "end_time": 30813.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30837.0,
      "end_time": 32806.0,
      "text": "Five stitches in his forehead."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33863.0,
      "end_time": 36936.0,
      "text": "At that moment, I felt like the worst teacher in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36960.0,
      "end_time": 39680.0,
      "text": "I really didn&#39;t know how to apologize."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39845.0,
      "end_time": 45556.0,
      "text": "Luckily, El Pulga is one of those people who takes things quite well."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46228.0,
      "end_time": 48752.0,
      "text": "And to this day, he says that I was the coach"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48776.0,
      "end_time": 51220.0,
      "text": "who left the most important mark on his career."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51244.0,
      "end_time": 53417.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53441.0,
      "end_time": 56723.0,
      "text": "The truth is, when I started working at the institute for the blind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56747.0,
      "end_time": 58499.0,
      "text": "I was surprised by a lot of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58926.0,
      "end_time": 62450.0,
      "text": "A lot of the things they did, I never imagined they could:"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62474.0,
      "end_time": 66396.0,
      "text": "they swam, did exercise, played cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66970.0,
      "end_time": 68624.0,
      "text": "They drank mate, and could pour it"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68648.0,
      "end_time": 70711.0,
      "text": "without burning themselves in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70736.0,
      "end_time": 72529.0,
      "text": "But when I saw them playing soccer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72553.0,
      "end_time": 73965.0,
      "text": "that was amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74672.0,
      "end_time": 78547.0,
      "text": "They had a dirt field, rusty goalposts and broken nets."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79540.0,
      "end_time": 82201.0,
      "text": "The blind who attended the institute would play their games there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82225.0,
      "end_time": 84800.0,
      "text": "just like I did at a field near my house."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84824.0,
      "end_time": 86916.0,
      "text": "But they played without being able to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87534.0,
      "end_time": 91150.0,
      "text": "The ball made a sound so they could locate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91390.0,
      "end_time": 94500.0,
      "text": "They had a guide behind the rival team&#39;s goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94740.0,
      "end_time": 96780.0,
      "text": "to know where to kick the ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96102.0,
      "end_time": 97980.0,
      "text": "And they used eye masks."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98400.0,
      "end_time": 100240.0,
      "text": "There were guys who could still see a little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100264.0,
      "end_time": 103419.0,
      "text": "and they wore eye masks so everyone was equal."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104524.0,
      "end_time": 109176.0,
      "text": "When I was more at ease with them, I asked for a mask myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109200.0,
      "end_time": 111846.0,
      "text": "I put it on and tried to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111870.0,
      "end_time": 113567.0,
      "text": "I had played soccer all my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114272.0,
      "end_time": 116318.0,
      "text": "This is where it got even more amazing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116342.0,
      "end_time": 119161.0,
      "text": "within two seconds, I didn&#39;t know where I was standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122126.0,
      "end_time": 125880.0,
      "text": "I had studied physical education because I loved high performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125904.0,
      "end_time": 128119.0,
      "text": "I started working at the institute by chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128143.0,
      "end_time": 130990.0,
      "text": "My other job was with the Argentinian National Rowing Team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131140.0,
      "end_time": 132669.0,
      "text": "and I felt that was my thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133262.0,
      "end_time": 135650.0,
      "text": "Here, everything was twice as hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135785.0,
      "end_time": 139540.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget the first day I did the warm-up with the team."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139564.0,
      "end_time": 141275.0,
      "text": "I lined them up in front of me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141300.0,
      "end_time": 144169.0,
      "text": "I used to do that with the rowing team --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144193.0,
      "end_time": 147448.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"OK, everyone bend down,\" going like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147472.0,
      "end_time": 149414.0,
      "text": "When I looked up, two guys were seated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149438.0,
      "end_time": 151747.0,
      "text": "three were lying down and others were squatting."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151771.0,
      "end_time": 153137.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153161.0,
      "end_time": 156523.0,
      "text": "How could I do here the same things I was doing there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158907.0,
      "end_time": 160290.0,
      "text": "It took me a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 160314.0,
      "end_time": 163778.0,
      "text": "I started looking for tools to learn from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163802.0,
      "end_time": 166370.0,
      "text": "from the teachers who worked with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 166394.0,
      "end_time": 171400.0,
      "text": "I learned I couldn&#39;t explain a play on a chalkboard like a coach does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171640.0,
      "end_time": 173844.0,
      "text": "but I could use a plastic tray and some bottle caps"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 173868.0,
      "end_time": 176237.0,
      "text": "so they could follow me by way of touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176779.0,
      "end_time": 179932.0,
      "text": "I also learned they could run on a track"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179956.0,
      "end_time": 181978.0,
      "text": "if I ran with them, holding a rope."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182656.0,
      "end_time": 185823.0,
      "text": "So we started looking for volunteers to help us run with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186312.0,
      "end_time": 188381.0,
      "text": "I was enjoying it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 189764.0,
      "end_time": 193560.0,
      "text": "and finding purpose and meaning in what we were doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193805.0,
      "end_time": 195907.0,
      "text": "It was hard at first, it was uncomfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195931.0,
      "end_time": 198740.0,
      "text": "but I decided to overcome the discomfort."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198980.0,
      "end_time": 199520.0,
      "text": "And there came a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 199544.0,
      "end_time": 202308.0,
      "text": "when it became the most fascinating job I&#39;d ever had."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203249.0,
      "end_time": 205606.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s when I wondered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 205630.0,
      "end_time": 209853.0,
      "text": "Why couldn&#39;t we be a high-performance team as well?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210966.0,
      "end_time": 212699.0,
      "text": "Of course, one thing was missing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212723.0,
      "end_time": 214793.0,
      "text": "I needed to find out what they wanted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 214817.0,
      "end_time": 217396.0,
      "text": "the real protagonists of this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218823.0,
      "end_time": 222325.0,
      "text": "Three hours of training, playing soccer on that field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222349.0,
      "end_time": 223959.0,
      "text": "were not going to be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223984.0,
      "end_time": 226119.0,
      "text": "We would have to train differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226143.0,
      "end_time": 229882.0,
      "text": "We started to train harder, and the results were great;"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 229906.0,
      "end_time": 231195.0,
      "text": "they asked for more."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231733.0,
      "end_time": 233855.0,
      "text": "I came to understand that they, too, wondered"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233879.0,
      "end_time": 235786.0,
      "text": "why they couldn&#39;t do high-performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 237151.0,
      "end_time": 241150.0,
      "text": "When we felt ready, we knocked at CENARD&#39;s door."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 241174.0,
      "end_time": 243914.0,
      "text": "CENARD is the National Center for High-Performance Sports"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 243938.0,
      "end_time": 245281.0,
      "text": "here in Argentina."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 245306.0,
      "end_time": 247723.0,
      "text": "It was hard to get them to hear what we had to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 247747.0,
      "end_time": 250203.0,
      "text": "But it was considerably more difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 250227.0,
      "end_time": 253993.0,
      "text": "to get the other athletes training there to consider us their equals."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 254662.0,
      "end_time": 256598.0,
      "text": "In fact, they would let us use the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 256622.0,
      "end_time": 258835.0,
      "text": "only when no other teams were using it."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 259367.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261311.00000000003,
      "text": "And we were known as \"the blind ones.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261724.0,
      "end_time": 264269.0,
      "text": "Not everyone knew exactly what we were doing there."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265622.0,
      "end_time": 269663.0,
      "text": "The 2006 World Championship was a turning point in the team&#39;s history."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270449.0,
      "end_time": 273233.0,
      "text": "It was held in Buenos Aires for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 273257.0,
      "end_time": 276560.0,
      "text": "It was our chance to show everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 278300.0,
      "text": "what we had been doing all that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 278947.0,
      "end_time": 280494.0,
      "text": "We made it to the finals."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 281200.0,
      "end_time": 282741.0,
      "text": "We were growing as a team."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283374.0,
      "end_time": 285393.0,
      "text": "It was us against Brazil in the finals."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286406.0,
      "end_time": 288612.0,
      "text": "They were the best team in the tournament."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 289330.0,
      "end_time": 291176.0,
      "text": "They won every game by a landslide."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292264.0,
      "end_time": 296803.0,
      "text": "Hardly anyone believed we could win that game."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 297942.0,
      "end_time": 299689.0,
      "text": "Hardly anyone -- except for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 300935.0,
      "end_time": 302809.0,
      "text": "During pre-game meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 302833.0,
      "end_time": 304476.0,
      "text": "in the locker room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304500.0,
      "end_time": 305901.0,
      "text": "during each warm-up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306592.0,
      "end_time": 308127.0,
      "text": "it smelled of victory."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310790.0,
      "end_time": 311531.0,
      "text": "I swear that smell exists."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 312433.0,
      "end_time": 315550.0,
      "text": "I smelled it several times with the team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315790.0,
      "end_time": 318355.0,
      "text": "but I remember it in particular, the day before we played that final."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 319328.0,
      "end_time": 322440.0,
      "text": "The Argentine Football Association had opened their doors to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322464.0,
      "end_time": 323930.0,
      "text": "We were training at AFA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323954.0,
      "end_time": 326448.0,
      "text": "where Ver√≥n, Higuain and Messi trained."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326472.0,
      "end_time": 327881.0,
      "text": "For the first time ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 329810.0,
      "end_time": 331461.0,
      "text": "we felt like a true national team."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 332214.0,
      "end_time": 334671.0,
      "text": "At 7:30pm, the day before the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 334695.0,
      "end_time": 338522.0,
      "text": "we were in the lounge discussing strategy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338547.0,
      "end_time": 341762.0,
      "text": "and a waiter knocks on the door, interrupting our conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 342646.0,
      "end_time": 344330.0,
      "text": "He suggested we go to church."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 344354.0,
      "end_time": 346154.0,
      "text": "He came to invite us to church."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347253.0,
      "end_time": 351115.0,
      "text": "I tried to get rid of him, saying it wasn&#39;t a good time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351139.0,
      "end_time": 353968.0,
      "text": "that we better leave it for another day."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353992.0,
      "end_time": 359483.0,
      "text": "He kept insisting, asking me to please let him take the guys to church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 359507.0,
      "end_time": 362729.0,
      "text": "because that day, a pastor who performed miracles would be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364400.0,
      "end_time": 367792.0,
      "text": "I was slightly afraid to ask what type of miracles he meant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367816.0,
      "end_time": 370510.0,
      "text": "and he replied nonchalantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 370760.0,
      "end_time": 372276.0,
      "text": "\"Coach, let me take the team to the church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372300.0,
      "end_time": 375653.0,
      "text": "and when we return, I guarantee that half of them will be able to see.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 376129.0,
      "end_time": 379177.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 380655.0,
      "end_time": 382101.0,
      "text": "Some of the guys laughed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 382125.0,
      "end_time": 385275.0,
      "text": "but imagine being a blind person and someone says that to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 385299.0,
      "end_time": 386683.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know what to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 386708.0,
      "end_time": 389352.0,
      "text": "I said nothing; it was an awkward silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 389376.0,
      "end_time": 391120.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t want to make him feel bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391144.0,
      "end_time": 393318.0,
      "text": "because he truly believed this could happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394320.0,
      "end_time": 395994.0,
      "text": "One of the players saved me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 396694.0,
      "end_time": 398640.0,
      "text": "when he stood up and confidently said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398664.0,
      "end_time": 400548.0,
      "text": "\"Juan,\" -- that was the kid&#39;s name --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 400572.0,
      "end_time": 403525.0,
      "text": "Gonza already told you it&#39;s not the best time to go to church."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 403549.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "Besides, let me make this clear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 405354.0,
      "end_time": 409236.0,
      "text": "if we go to that church, and I end up being able to see when we return,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 412277.0,
      "text": "I will beat you so hard if I can&#39;t play tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 412302.0,
      "end_time": 414600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 414300.0,
      "end_time": 420890.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 424998.0,
      "end_time": 428942.0,
      "text": "Juan left, laughing in resignation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 428966.0,
      "end_time": 431120.0,
      "text": "and we continued with our pregame talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 431687.0,
      "end_time": 434580.0,
      "text": "That night when I went to sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 434604.0,
      "end_time": 437925.0,
      "text": "I began to dream about the next day&#39;s game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 437949.0,
      "end_time": 440628.0,
      "text": "imagining what could happen, how we would play."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 440652.0,
      "end_time": 443108.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s when I noticed that smell of victory"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 443132.0,
      "end_time": 444346.0,
      "text": "I mentioned a while ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 444806.0,
      "end_time": 446969.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s because at that moment, I thought:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 446993.0,
      "end_time": 451676.0,
      "text": "if the other players had the same desire as Diego going into the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 452261.0,
      "end_time": 454261.0,
      "text": "it was impossible for us not to win."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 455779.0,
      "end_time": 457961.0,
      "text": "The next day was going to be wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 458446.0,
      "end_time": 461502.0,
      "text": "We got up at 9am, the game was at 7pm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461526.0,
      "end_time": 463747.0,
      "text": "and we were already eager to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 464227.0,
      "end_time": 470920.0,
      "text": "We left AFA, and the bus was full of flags that people had given to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 470608.0,
      "end_time": 472767.0,
      "text": "We were talking about the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 472791.0,
      "end_time": 475331.0,
      "text": "and we could hear people honking and cheering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 475355.0,
      "end_time": 478665.0,
      "text": "\"Go Murci√©lagos! Today&#39;s the day! The final challenge!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 478689.0,
      "end_time": 482410.0,
      "text": "The guys asked me, \"Do they know us? Do they know we&#39;re playing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483134.0,
      "end_time": 486542.0,
      "text": "Some people followed the bus to CENARD."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 487237.0,
      "end_time": 490827.0,
      "text": "We arrived and found an amazing scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 491247.0,
      "end_time": 494313.0,
      "text": "In the corridor leading from the locker room to the game field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 494337.0,
      "end_time": 496289.0,
      "text": "I was walking with Silvio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 496313.0,
      "end_time": 499401.0,
      "text": "who was holding onto my shoulder, so I could guide him."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 499425.0,
      "end_time": 501688.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, there were no gates along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 501712.0,
      "end_time": 502712.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 502736.0,
      "end_time": 505848.0,
      "text": "When we reached the field, he asked me about everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 505872.0,
      "end_time": 507808.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t want to miss a single detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 507832.0,
      "end_time": 511651.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Tell me what you see, tell me who&#39;s playing the drums.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 511675.0,
      "end_time": 515570.0,
      "text": "I tried to explain what was happening with as much detail as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 515594.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520394.00000000006,
      "text": "I told him, \"The stands are packed, a lot of people couldn&#39;t get in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 520418.0,
      "end_time": 523120.0,
      "text": "there are blue and white balloons all over the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 523350.0,
      "end_time": 527176.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re opening a giant Argentine flag that covers the entire grandstand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 527201.0,
      "end_time": 529298.0,
      "text": "Suddenly, he cuts me off and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 529322.0,
      "end_time": 533157.0,
      "text": "\"Do you see a flag that says &#39;San Pedro&#39;?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 534674.0,
      "end_time": 536279.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the city where he lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 536641.0,
      "end_time": 538456.0,
      "text": "I started looking into the stands"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 538480.0,
      "end_time": 540989.0,
      "text": "and I spotted a little white flag"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 541130.0,
      "end_time": 544630.0,
      "text": "with lettering done in black spray paint, that read:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 544870.0,
      "end_time": 547689.0,
      "text": "\"Silvio, your family and all of San Pedro are here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 548227.0,
      "end_time": 550959.0,
      "text": "I told him that and he replied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 550983.0,
      "end_time": 555310.0,
      "text": "\"That&#39;s my mom, tell me where she is, I want to I wave at her.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 555564.0,
      "end_time": 556996.0,
      "text": "I pointed him toward the flag"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 557200.0,
      "end_time": 559566.0,
      "text": "and showed him with his arm where they were sitting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 559590.0,
      "end_time": 561574.0,
      "text": "and he waved his arms in that direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 561598.0,
      "end_time": 564689.0,
      "text": "About 20 or 30 people stood up and gave him an ovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 565341.0,
      "end_time": 566730.0,
      "text": "When that happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 566754.0,
      "end_time": 569790.0,
      "text": "I saw how his face changed, how moved he was."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 569615.0,
      "end_time": 571461.0,
      "text": "It was moving for me, too;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 572106.0,
      "end_time": 574296.0,
      "text": "two seconds later, I had a lump in my throat."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 575318.0,
      "end_time": 578603.0,
      "text": "It was strange -- I felt both the excitement of what was happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 578628.0,
      "end_time": 581786.0,
      "text": "and the anger and the anguish that he could not see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 583457.0,
      "end_time": 588540.0,
      "text": "A few days later when I told him what I had experienced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 589266.0,
      "end_time": 592510.0,
      "text": "he tried to reassure me, saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 592534.0,
      "end_time": 595111.0,
      "text": "\"Gonza, don&#39;t feel bad, I could see them."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 595135.0,
      "end_time": 597852.0,
      "text": "Differently, but I swear to you that I saw them all.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 599248.0,
      "end_time": 600644.0,
      "text": "The game started."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 600668.0,
      "end_time": 603506.0,
      "text": "We could not fail; it was the final."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603530.0,
      "end_time": 605954.0,
      "text": "The audience was quiet, like here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 605979.0,
      "end_time": 607623.0,
      "text": "because in soccer for the blind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 607647.0,
      "end_time": 610646.0,
      "text": "the public has to be quiet so the players can hear the ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 611640.0,
      "end_time": 613813.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re only allowed to cheer when the game is over."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 614265.0,
      "end_time": 616906.0,
      "text": "And when there were eight minutes to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 617747.0,
      "end_time": 621194.0,
      "text": "the crowd did all the cheering they hadn&#39;t done in the first 32 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 621218.0,
      "end_time": 624847.0,
      "text": "When pigeon-toed Silvio nailed the ball at an angle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 624871.0,
      "end_time": 626959.0,
      "text": "they cheered with all their heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 626983.0,
      "end_time": 628556.0,
      "text": "in an incredible way."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 630848.0,
      "end_time": 635466.0,
      "text": "Today, if you go to CENARD, you&#39;ll see a huge poster on the door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635490.0,
      "end_time": 637411.0,
      "text": "with a photo of our team, Los Murci√©lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 638227.0,
      "end_time": 642871.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re a model national team, everyone in CENARD knows who they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 642895.0,
      "end_time": 645478.0,
      "text": "and after having won two World Championships"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 645502.0,
      "end_time": 646899.0,
      "text": "and two Paralympic medals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 646923.0,
      "end_time": 649382.0,
      "text": "no one doubts they are high-performance athletes."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 649406.0,
      "end_time": 656550.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 664100.0,
      "end_time": 666100.0,
      "text": "(Applause ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 667148.0,
      "end_time": 670836.0,
      "text": "I was lucky to train this team for 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 670860.0,
      "end_time": 674520.0,
      "text": "first as a trainer and later as their coach."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 675110.0,
      "end_time": 679969.0,
      "text": "I feel that they&#39;ve given me much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 679993.0,
      "end_time": 681412.0,
      "text": "than what I&#39;ve given them."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 682209.0,
      "end_time": 688236.0,
      "text": "Last year, they asked me to coach another national team, Power Soccer."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 689394.0,
      "end_time": 693228.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a national team of young men who play soccer in wheelchairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 693824.0,
      "end_time": 696871.0,
      "text": "They use motorized wheelchairs that they drive with a joystick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 696895.0,
      "end_time": 699453.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t have enough strength in their arms"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 699477.0,
      "end_time": 700770.0,
      "text": "to use conventional chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 700794.0,
      "end_time": 704504.0,
      "text": "They added a bumper to the chair, a safeguard that protects their feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 704528.0,
      "end_time": 706647.0,
      "text": "while allowing them to kick the ball."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 707548.0,
      "end_time": 711715.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the first time that, instead of being the spectators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 711739.0,
      "end_time": 713556.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re now the main characters."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 713580.0,
      "end_time": 718790.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the first time their parents, friends and siblings can see them play."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 719760.0,
      "end_time": 722103.0,
      "text": "For me, it&#39;s a new challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 722127.0,
      "end_time": 725371.0,
      "text": "with the same discomfort, insecurity, and fear I had"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 725395.0,
      "end_time": 727371.0,
      "text": "when I started working with the blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 727860.0,
      "end_time": 730577.0,
      "text": "But I approach it all from a more experienced position."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 730601.0,
      "end_time": 735803.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why from day one, I treat them as athletes on the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 735827.0,
      "end_time": 738437.0,
      "text": "and off the field, I try to put myself in their shoes"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 738461.0,
      "end_time": 739888.0,
      "text": "and behave without prejudice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 739912.0,
      "end_time": 743869.0,
      "text": "because treating them naturally feels best to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 745326.0,
      "end_time": 749714.0,
      "text": "Both teams play soccer; something once unthinkable for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 750303.0,
      "end_time": 754590.0,
      "text": "They had to adapt the rules to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 755129.0,
      "end_time": 757653.0,
      "text": "And both teams broke the same rule --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 757677.0,
      "end_time": 760449.0,
      "text": "the one that said they couldn&#39;t play soccer."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 761589.0,
      "end_time": 765813.0,
      "text": "When you see them play, you see competition, not disability."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 766568.0,
      "end_time": 769722.0,
      "text": "The problem starts when the game is over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 769746.0,
      "end_time": 771221.0,
      "text": "and they leave the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 771245.0,
      "end_time": 773741.0,
      "text": "Then they step in to play our game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 773765.0,
      "end_time": 777718.0,
      "text": "in a society whose rules don&#39;t really take them into account"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 777743.0,
      "end_time": 778908.0,
      "text": "or care for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 779520.0,
      "end_time": 781340.0,
      "text": "I learned from sports"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 781364.0,
      "end_time": 784996.0,
      "text": "that disability greatly depends on the rules of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 785512.0,
      "end_time": 789575.0,
      "text": "I believe that if we change some of the rules of our game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 789600.0,
      "end_time": 791882.0,
      "text": "we can make life a little easier for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 793209.0,
      "end_time": 798890.0,
      "text": "We all know there are people with disabilities; we see them daily."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 798644.0,
      "end_time": 801605.0,
      "text": "But by having no direct contact with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 801629.0,
      "end_time": 805179.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not aware of the problems they face every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 805203.0,
      "end_time": 807310.0,
      "text": "like how hard it is for them to get on a bus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 807334.0,
      "end_time": 808984.0,
      "text": "find a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 809900.0,
      "end_time": 810162.0,
      "text": "take the subway"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 810186.0,
      "end_time": 811336.0,
      "text": "or cross the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 812367.0,
      "end_time": 815538.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s true that there is an increasing social responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 815562.0,
      "end_time": 819408.0,
      "text": "regarding the inclusion of people with disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 820466.0,
      "end_time": 822959.0,
      "text": "But I think it&#39;s still not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 822983.0,
      "end_time": 826210.0,
      "text": "I think change needs to come from every one of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 826460.0,
      "end_time": 829692.0,
      "text": "First, by leaving behind our indifference toward the disabled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 829716.0,
      "end_time": 833670.0,
      "text": "and then by respecting the rules that do take them into account."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 833910.0,
      "end_time": 834848.0,
      "text": "They are few, but they do exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 837158.0,
      "end_time": 840158.0,
      "text": "I cracked a blind man&#39;s head open -- El Pulga&#39;s head."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 840669.0,
      "end_time": 844523.0,
      "text": "I can assure you these two teams opened mine as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 844547.0,
      "end_time": 845984.0,
      "text": "They taught me that above all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 846800.0,
      "end_time": 848132.0,
      "text": "you have to get out there and play every game"
    },
    {
